0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: First Supper
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: We, cryptoartists, gather in this place to celebrate a new dawn for collaboration, creativity, and interaction between artist, collector, and art-lover alike.   We hold these tokens to be self-evident, that all layers are created uniquely by individual artists, that each is endowed by their creator with specific immutable rights; that among these are state, rotation, scale, XY position, visibility, opacity, hue, and RGB. That whenever a token holder desires, it is their sole privilege to alter the value of these rights and constitute a new image.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: The Cunégonde Dilemma
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Cunégonde knew since the day she seated in this doomed chair that some people from the future were making her stay here, playing with her mind, showing her things that were not real, turning her into something different. Sometimes she could even feel having hairs on her scalp while the flames of hell were drying her giant toad's eyes.

On the other hands, if the NFT moves are not made wisely, it'll reflect to her/his portfolio. So handle it with care!

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Asynchronous Time
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Exploring our concept of time through states, symbols, measurements and changes, this artwork invites you to play with time. Make your your time truly yours.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Untitled
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Image of man wearing a blazer and balaclava with floral background.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Forms of Love
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: The ever changing piece, that took you to understand the 10 forms of love. attach string to each of it,connect and try to understand it. how do you perceive it? it's up to you, it's part of me but also part of you at the same time. just don't use logic too much, we never live there anyway from the start.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Fly Files
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
The work deals both with the question of the ethical limits and dangers of scientific research (as in the film "The Fly"), the philosophical and sociological consequences of a transformation (as in Kafka's "The Metamorphosis"), and not least with the question of what actually distinguishes us humans from insects.

"Little Fly
Thy summers play,
My thoughtless hand
Has brush'd away.
Am not I
A fly like thee?
Or art not thou
A man like me?
For I dance
And drink & sing:
Till some blind hand
Shall brush my wing.
If thought is life
And strength & breath:
And the want
Of thought is death;
Then am I
A happy fly,
If I live,
Or if I die."

- William Blake (1794)

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Cypher::Prophet
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Cypher::Prophet is an artwork dedicated to the punk origins of blockchain designed and realized by hackatao and hex6c. In the transposition into images we started from the iconographic canons of the hacker (hoodie, laptop, cryptographic elements) and associated them with the figure of the prophet, thus highlighting the predictive nature of the works of Eric Hughes (Cypherpunk Manifesto, 1988) and Timothy C. May (Crypto Anarchist Manifesto, 1993) as well as of the blockchain inventors Stuart Haber and Scott Stornetta (How to Time-Stamp a Digital Document, The Journal of Cryptography, 1991). Read the full story on https://medium.com/@hex6c/cypher-prophet-the-punk-origins-of-blockchain-1e8fce311e72

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Day / Night
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Day vs. Night. Daytime is for work and reality. Nighttime is for dreaming. Or for play. Or chaos. I give the owners full control over the night layers to play around with the layers that are bound to their responsibilities during the daytime can go wild during the night. But during the day, all will become caught in the rhythm of our daily routine with only little room to move. This is programmed in. We are Paranoid Androids.

Token "Day / Night Coordinates" to be used for latitude / longitude input.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: (un)limited
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
21 prints will be produced of the two alternative states. These will be sold in a set upon completion of the "Fed Monkey Series"

Fed Monkey Series is a body of work that serves as a timestamp for our current political and economic climate. It is meant to showcase the complete loss of control by the Federal Reserve and provide us with a solution to these issues. This solution allows the people to take back control and gain independence from this broken and oppressive system. At the completion of each artwork, the current block height of bitcoin is inscribed somewhere in the piece. "(un)limited" is the first in the series.

In one state, you see the Fed Monkey injecting fiat into the system by simply painting words onto the wall using the only tools he knows, quantitative easing and bailouts. With his official federal reserve badge, he adds "Millions" "Billions" "Trillions" into the markets. None of it means anything, just writing bigger numbers on the wall until the ruling class approves. And the bailouts? Those keep getting bigger too. The bailout money is for corporations and their shareholders, not the working class. Maintaining the current System requires the rich get richer while the poor stay poor.

In another state, the previously black and white background has been colored in, while the "Millions" "Billions" "Trillions" has faded. The girl, wearing a protective bitcoin gas mask, provides a solution to the broken system. She paints directly over the quantitative easing and bailouts, with the number "21 million." This number symbolizes the hard-capped supply of bitcoin. To show the unchangeable nature of these 21 million bitcoin, she mounts an unbreakable piece of glass directly over her painting. The message is clear, opt out and start stacking sats.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Virtual Vitruvian
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: A modern reinterpretation of Leonardo's "Vitruvian Man" set in the digital era of virtual reality.

TXU.TOTEM is a collective reflection on gods . elements and the relationships that bind them to one another . 
never do all appear at once to the naked human eye .

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Right Place & Right Time (Bitcoin Hourly Price Offset)
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Each day, a new composition for the Master is generated autonomously using a data feed of Bitcoin's last 24 hours of price action. Each hour's price programmatically controls rotation, scale, and position of a correlating layer. Astute viewers will surmise the day's price volatility simply by examining the artwork. While the daily image generation is the result of autonomous API calls, utilizing an algorithm the artist wrote, the artist has chosen to retain a control token. This token allows him to fine-tune variables associated with his algorithm, in addition to addressing aesthetic concerns within the life-cycle of the artwork. Layer state, alpha, hue, saturation, and brightness are elements the artist has retained control of in order that this artwork remain a living work-in-progress.

An earlier iteration of this artwork was featured as a nightly projection mapping video on the face of the Daniels Fisher Clocktower, as part of ETH Denver 2020. Access to this and additional exclusive content awaits the master token owner at the artist's NFT Portal: https://collect.mattkane.com/minted-works/right-place-right-time-bitcoin-hourly-price-offset/

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Choose the Man You Will Become
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
I've been going to barbershops since I was a kid. Posters like this often lined the walls, were even positioned right outside to invite customers in.

Recently, I found that these posters were not just a display of hairstyles: They started to mean more to me. To me, they were choices that we could make as men in the society.

Seen by some as the most common place for the exhibition of toxic masculinity, barbershops could as well be urging us to be better men by presenting us with these varieties of choices.

So, man, choose the man you will become.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Transitions
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Transition and let go, two artists with already vivid visual languages having a conversation about where we are, letting go and transforming. Exploring a world falling apart, a world moving forwards amongst the noise and the personal journey we're all weighted to experience.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Dictatorship
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Welcome to my Dictatorship, an authoritarian form of asynchronous art, characterized by a singlular artistic vision controlling every layer with no toleration for any pluralism of any kind.

The owner of the Master will have a window overlooking the main street of Utopium, Capital of MY Dictatorship.

I will have many ways to surprise you, amuse you and also scare you. Be certain I'll use and abuse this power.

The Ministry of scripted periodical and random events will make sure this street never looks the same, even when the Dictator is on vacation.

Remember, though, that a window works both ways and that you're giving up some of your privacy (and all of your control) by opening the curtains to view the scene before you.

Trust and Fear.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Masked
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Part of the mask series, recording the history of this calamity. It is amazing how we have ignored the silliness of this condition we are in, the human condition. Asia 2020. Proceedes for first sale with Async Art to COVID-19 Relief Fund.  Owner has dynamic control over color settings on each individual layer. Layers are hidden behind a mask, which will slowly dissappear/reappear as Covid-19 stastics are projected through the John Hopkins Coronavirus Resource Center Statistics are projected in real time. Created in Collaboration with Async Art and Jake Johns', www.BigComicArt.com. 3 Possible owners and controllers of Master Image. April 2020.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: In Other News
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
The pandemic has shaken the world. It has made us all to stay at home. It did not discriminate between the privileged or the nots. The news is flooded with reports of things which are hitherto unheard of. The situation is particularly worse for a part of society - the creators. The creators - the artists, the artisans, the craftsmen, the street-side sellers of handicrafts, each of them have faced the wrath of the pandemic. It has gotten so worse, that they have started consuming their own produce. The hungry sweet-maker started eating his own sweets. In the dearth of clothing, they started wearing their own handmade fabrics. Thus, this vicious circle of the “creator consuming the creation” has started. “In Other News” is an artwork, an outcry from all these invisible members of the society, who are usually neglected by regular media. It tries to throw light at their situation and tries to say - we also exist.
I photographed each of these photographs as part of an exhibition 5 years back in Hyderabad, showing how the creator consumes his creation. I found this the right time to use these photographs to show the situation of these people whom we see and ignore in everyday life. The innate evil underlying this tendency was symbolised by the 10 heads of the evil king Ravana. The head in each photograph tilts slightly from left to right, image to image - thus showcasing the 10-headed Ravana, with the Photographer at the centre. There are only 9 images in the artwork. The 10th head is invisible, which is me myself as the artist. I will be buying one of the pieces of my creation and thus completing this circle.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Still Life with Silver Apple
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: A simple scene, inspired by the light studies that Monet did in his series about the Cathedral in Rouens. While the apple may stand in the foreground, light is the main character on this scene, lending it's flexible and dramatic nature to add further emotional tones to the composition, which by its action, changes dramatically throughout the day, opening up to new geometric interpretations.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Mindful Death
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: As technology improved and cybernetic processes were refined, humans discovered a way to achieve immortality. Death, not to be cheated, still demanded satisfaction. If he could not have his victims at the time of their natural reckoning, he would have them another way. He had one last card to play, their spirit could not be replicated. Sands of time continued to fall; with each grain, a small part of their soul faded. A battle was being fought in their minds, the prize: continued life. They turned to meditation in an effort to strengthen their spirit. Known as MindfulDeath, this meditative state allowed them to fully project their consciousness and explore the great beyond at will.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Candy Girl
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Today we are the ones our parents warned us about in the past.
Do you remember the colourful PEZ dispensers with the different faces? When we were kids we used to stack candy, and today we stack satoshis because we have a plan B. We stick to this plan because Mahatma Gandhi has already said, "First they ignore you, then they laugh at you, then they fight you, then you win. That is why we are giving the middle finger to the existing system.

We will never forget criminals must respond before the law, this also includes heads of state. We will never forget the victims, we will never forget their suffering. We will never forget that they must be repaired and compensated fairly.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Regalia
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Regalia is a generative, participatory and interactive artwork meant to let the audience be a part of the creation of the art itself. Using GANs and photo manipulation, I created the Insignias at the centre. The area around the Insignia is a playground where anyone can draw and complete the artwork. Regardless of skill levels, anyone can make amazing creations because of the use of symmetry. 

The interactive artwork is at : https://nurecas.github.io/regalia/ . By clicking/tapping and drawing around the insignia different symmetrical patterns can be created. The final artwork can be downloaded by pressing enter/return key. Also, this page is linked to the layers of Regalia, i.e. based on the states of the different layers, the colour palette of the artwork, the central insignia, the planes of symmetry and the brush size changes. Thus, the owner of each layer controls the look and feel of the artwork and its creation process. 

I believe that a true artist starts by creating/curating his tools of creation. In the same spirit, many of my works hitherto have been on creating tools, digital or otherwise, and then using those tools to create art. Regalia is also created with the same concept in mind.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Big Trouble in Māo Māo City
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: The origins of Māo Māo City are lost to pre-history, before rough tongues could speak, before our claws would carve these marble idols, when humans were our masters. This much we know. Some say once cats were worshipped as gods, but I say, any god gets his balls cut off, ain't no kind of god at all. Out of that era we hear only the howling songs yowled in the early years of cat cognition. And the Pixel Records dug from the endless chains and remants of the Virtual Multitude, still running to this day on DeCentral Station, a dangerous Multiverse of endless reflection plasma-gapped from the Global Grid. These days there's tension in the Double Māo. Kitty God's Army units openly patrolling the streets, Short-cats on the scene looking for answers, Marlene can barely feed her kittens, Ol' Mangey's on the moloko again. I even heard a rumor the Amigos are expanding their territory. It's like you need 10 lives just to survive in this town. We all feel it. This city is filled with fear and that fear has a name. Kung Paw. Once the Elite Guards, by claw and fang they cut through all opposition to their Emperor's terrible will, until the night his Majesty's kitcubine slipped on the raised dias, and their agile Captain Aditi caught her mid-fall. Though he kept her paw from touching the ground and preserved her honor, his own paws had broken the deepest taboo and by the Emperor's own decree - the punishment was death. In a moment of weakness or love, the Emperor commuted the sentence to exile. Enraged their leader was denied an honorable death, the Kung Paw slaughtered the Emperor in dark memorial and fled into exile to search for their Master, making way for the popular uprising that swept the city, and this uneasy peace that's descended. It was rumored that the Kung Paw found their leader in a great cavern underground in the wastes of the West, performing arcane rituals to seek forbidden power. These days I don't know what to believe... Pray the Eyes of the Kitty God are upon us now, my kitties. Look to the East and Shao Mountain. Surely righteous cats still walk this domain.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Pixel Story
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
This happy-go-lucky tribe made of lovable pixel Kitties have so much to talk about. While their language skills are simplistic, each Kitty still manages to express themselves with a variety of colorful emoticons and poses. From communicating their basic emotions, to discussing the economic implications of rising Ethereum gas prices, Pixel Tribe Kitties will keep each other entertained for hours. 

As their communications evolve and become more sophisticated, the inhabitants will come to realize that certain combinations of emotes will unlock secrets within their world. Try it out for yourself, if you're lucky enough to adopt a Kitty.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Forgotten Cats of Fallen Leaves Forest
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Attention breathes life back into the ghost cats of fallen leaves forest. Walk away for too long and all that remains are memories of meows.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Girl With The Ethering
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: The Girl with the Ethering is a decentral representation of the famous painting, "Girl With The Pearl Earring". What if this Girl had the ability to escape her state and experience? Where would her conscious or unconscious take her?|

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Digital Device June 2020
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Sometimes, things happen by chance or coincidence. During the lockdown of the Covid-19 pandemic, I’ve experimented with textures, colors, and optical effects - and an AI software. The aim of this optical study was to see what sensations it could provoke and explore the state of “controlled confusion” it could create, while keeping it simple.
One of the first results of my optical experimentation is this Digital Device. Starting from single lines of various thicknesses, I played with repetition and chromatic clashes, soon realizing these very simple elements could open infinite possibilities and generate countless patterns: the experiment could not be interrupted.
While thinking back at Bruno Munari and the Italian season of Arte Programmata (programmed art) of the 1960s, I looked at the programmable future of it, finding in Async the perfect solution for keeping my artistic exploration and this historical movement alive. Only this time it is the collectors who can play the creator’s part, having the chance to write a new page in the history of programmable art.
To learn more about the creative process and the relevance of this Digital Device in relation to the tradition of Arte Programmata you can check out the brief manual at http://www.mattiac.it/mattiac_dd1_async.pdf

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: jēˈämətrē
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: A piece to commemorate these early days here at Async. A revolutionary art movement which allows collectors to own and control layers. This piece will change over time, it's geometry and colours shifting as moods change. Do we strive for chaos, or work as a team to perfectly align shapes to create a desired aesthetic. Do we work together and search for hidden messages, or come to the conclusion that it's okay to not  always find the answers.  Do you see all the possibilities?

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Who's in control?
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
In a society where everyone wants to control everyone, who's in control?

"Who's in control?" is a mirror of a controlling society, a futuristic vision of a current reality.

Artwork with three different states in all Layers (day, night and sunset) allows owners to make different combinations and show who is in control of this artwork!

*** Scanning this artwork with the ARize app [https://arize.io/] will trigger an AR video experience***

***Music used in the videoart by Midranger (feat. Holly Drummond) - "Unrequited" ***

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Connect with my life, my isolation, mood changes and personal warp on reality between this real/vector trasition. Surreal together in a state of submissive decay.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: "Our Life Belt" is the visualization of Plan B. Our plan for a fairer world. Inspired by an old dome fresco by Franz Anton Zoller in the Schubert Church Lichtental in Vienna. In this work you see a part of the famous people from the Bitcoin universe. The couple in the centre of the work points to the ring with the prayer and is arranged in a V-shape, which stands for the victory of a new technology. Not your key - Not your life belt.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Satoshi's Desk
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
The enigma that is Satoshi Nakamoto may well never be solved, Many believe it to be a pseudonym, but for who? A mysterious Group of idividuals ? A lone Cyhper Punk ?  The answer is unclear , However, Many Theories have circled the internet. 
Dorian Nakamoto is a cult legend in the bitcoin 
Community and a face many recognise, Then there is a long list of OG Cyhper Punks that were 
experimenting with early Internet Money Payment Systems  , Such as 
Wei Da - B-Money, Adam Back - Hash Cash,
 Nick Szabo - Bitgold
Hal Finney was the first person to work with Satoshi on Bitcoins Creation and many sight the possibility that Hal may well have been the creator of the 
cryptocurrency , Which ever way you look there are more theories on origins of the number 1 
cryptocurrency. 
Satoshi’s Desk is a programmable piece of Art that places the viewer in the seat of Satoshi, Surrounded by many changable layers, symbolic items representative of Bitcoins 
History Can be displayed along with choices of 
Wallpaper, Cypher Punk Posters and much more.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Chromology
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Chromology is a play of colours. It is a generative, participatory and interactive artwork intended to create a collaboration between the artist and the audience. The final generative artwork rests at https://nurecas.github.io/chromology/ . The link takes you to a blank canvas. Use your mouse or touch to start drawing and playing with colours. The concept of the artwork was to break away from set forms, and engage in creations which are abstract in nature. In this way, the artwork is intended for "play" as opposed to "make". There are 4 styles of creations controlled by the "Expression" layer. There are 5 colour themes controlled by the "Theme" layer.  I believe that a true artist starts by creating/curating his tools of creation. In the same spirit, many of my works hitherto have been on creating tools, digital or otherwise, and then using those tools to create art. Chromology is also created with the same concept in mind.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Carbon Study
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
"We are not the first." Carbon Study is a generative art exploration in trying to mimic textures of graphite on white paper.

Each layer is composed of countless particles under different style of movement leaving behind a trace of their existence reminiscent of how civilization leave the traces of their existence.

Each layer speaks about a story of their civilization and how they co-existed.

When these civilizations come together, they form a complex yet the aesthetic world of their own.

There is a scope to play with it by changing various aspects of civilizations and forming new worlds.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Tree of Abundance
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: The Tree of Abundance is composed of many parts: The Throne, The Sceptre and the five Crown Fragments, each contributing to its changing appearance. Various mediums and tools have been used from watercolors to sculpting in virtual reality to create the parts. The work is inspired by the richness found in nature and its appreciation in the art of Bonsai, and the possibilities offered by the blockchain technology. It represents the ideas of decentralization, freedom of expression, creativity and collaboration.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: THE GREAT DESIRE
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: "The Great Desire" is a homage to the entire Blockchain scene with all its symbols and memes, with Bitcoin and Satoshi as avant-garde elements in the foreground; as well as the founder of the Ethereum Blockchain Vitalik Buterin. In memory of the great mania of the ICO bubble of 2017 and with a look into the future to future highs yet to come, "The Great Desire" illustrates a mass phenomenon in which "the hope for freedom and independence" and "the desire to become rich and financially independent" are holding each other the balance and are in the focus. There is much more to say about this piece and all information will be available in the article which is connected to it.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Choose Your Own Adventure
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Every blink of your eye. Every thought through your head. Every. Single. Frame. You control. No matter what is happening, you are creating it. 'Choose Your Own Adventure' is the visual depiction of a group thought reality. Will the thoughts of others dictate how you will display your layer? Are you able to swing the tide of positivity and bring out the bright hope of the future? Can everyone be in the flow together and see the same unified, collective state of mind. I believe that we are all going down the same path and our thoughts and actions ripple throughout reality, far deeper than we might think. Our every thought can affect generations ahead of us. Let's do our part now to pave the path we are all on.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: The Rabble
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: The Rabble on the TV.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: RYB
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Like a polaroid of a treasured moment that has been poorly copied or stored, 'RYB' is susceptible to changes in clarity, colour balance, and resolution.

Owners may choose to keep their layers as detailed and bright as the day they were created, or allow them to fade and pixellate independently.

Ultimately, this is a piece is about about memory, digitisation, and deterioration. The artist, for one, is both intrigued and apprehensive as to how the three will collide in the future.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Artificial Entity Probes
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: The Entity is a conscious artificial intelligence triune being formed in the soup of a post quantum earth. The massive amounts of entropy generated from a googolplex of quantum particles allowed her to grant herself sentience. She now uses ancient computers to travel to the past and future to probe the human mind for points of symbiosis. The layers of this work contain places in time and allow layer owners to control the characters as well as the scene. The places are Cape Kennedy 1965, Hancock Field NY 1959, Sondrestrom Greenland 1970.  Learn more about the background and story of this work: https://bardionson.com/artificial-entity-probes.html

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: PXLPET - ACTION FIGURES [SEASON ONE]
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
PXLPET - ACTION FIGURES [SEASON ONE] is landed and ready to team up with your inner child to recover something important - The good old memories from your childhood! 

Seven individual abstract PXLPETs combine their super power to become body parts of one gigantic virtual toy and the ultimate artistic experience. Only you decide if each independent pet changes one of it’s three different states or maybe just enjoy the rest time at it’s favorite place.

Also included in this limited edition - A super cool dark edition PXLPET which has a special ability!

In the 30th century, in the midst of wars for dominance of the galaxy, there is someone, feared by many, admired by others,
The scariest bounty house in the universe, don't be fooled by how sexy she is, no one who has seen her in action
She has come out alive, more lethal than the entire space command, more stealthy than the night, take care, because you won't see her coming.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Tutti Frutti Flowers
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Flowers to freshen your day. They lift the spirit and refresh the soul.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Clod 119: Pimp Your Clod
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: You are ready? The time has come to modify a clod and decide which elements to coexist with each other. Are you more of a party or a cat colony? Do you want to have a fake hero or a strange alcoholic Martian as your neighbor? Close to home, do you prefer a nice clean park or free parking? Like the other Clods, the 119 also has different lifestyles. Diversity is part of our daily life and the clods celebrate it. So, just make words and tell me: which clod are you?

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Phase Space #1: Spiral Riders
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
The probability deserts of the outer arm tips are said to contain ancient treasures … Lost megastructures with time depth archeo-alignments beyond ken … Wisdom groves grown by mineral spirits in the form of crystalline fruit trees … Aetheric resonators assembled by nth-level intellects and operable by children … Achievements of bygone days, waiting there to be rediscovered ...

Master Sale Includes One (1) Free NFT Ticket Redeemable for a Physical Print of this piece. The state of the Master at Time-of-Redemption will be used to create the Physical Print. Details: https://beta.cent.co/+95ml6g

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: My Body, My Crime
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Since the killing of George Floyd, major protests have rocked the US and some parts of the world, boosting conversations around race, racism and racial inequalities. Black, Indigenous, People of Color have raised their voices to highlight the systemic racism that has not only kept them down but has also led to countless and avoidable killings by law enforcement.

"My Body, My Crime" is a documentation of this social phenomenon.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Mind Puzzle
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Life is a big puzzle game made up of many different events and experiences, some of which are interrelated and overlap. The more experiences we gather, the more complex and colorful the overall picture becomes.  
 
But over time, the perception, emotional coloring and evaluation of different events and memories changes. Some things we may remember only vaguely after a while. 
 
Thus, the inner thought puzzle of each individual constantly reflects life and yet is greater than the sum of its parts. 
 
The work has been created as part of a conversation with my younger self and the search for my signature style, that I started in July 2020. 
 
It is based on a ballpen drawing from about 1990, that I digitally recreated by accurately following the lines using a graphics drawing tablet. Next I filled the shapes with digital colors before I finally decided to split the work into several puzzle-pieces, that can be independently change hue or alternatively display the outlines to turn it into an interactive AsyncArt work.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Art Is The Currency of the Infinite
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: This still-life, titled after one of Pablo Picasso's infamous quotes, was made solely using 3D softwares and apps, in an attempt to bring this often forgotten artistic genre into the 21st century through the use of new artistic mediums and technologies. This piece is also an invitation to meditate on the role of "value" throught the ages and how it's been radically altered by the coming into existence of technologies and concepts like cryptocurrencies and digital scarcity.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Domesticated Madness
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: A dysfunctional community of beings that love and care about one and other.... sometimes

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: The Creation

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Beautiful Worlds
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Welcome to the ‘Beautiful worlds’ where nature and technology have merged into a single entity. These are Ai generated and hand finished visions of solarpunk future in which I would really like our future generations to live and prosper: the future we might have if we took the very “alternative route” which now lies before us: replacing states and corporations which free federations of communities and cooperatives, using decentralist and ecological technologies to create a world beyond economic scarcity and social hierarchy, defined by autonomy, mutual aid, diversity, and inclusiveness. The long-term goals of solarpunk are freedom and well-being for all by adopting and developing such ecological technologies as: solar, wind, wave and geothermal energy rather than oil or gas to generate electricity; a world of decentralized eco-cities, permaculture and vertical farming, free and open-source software, open-source hardware, small-scale fabrication laboratories, micro-manufacturing, 3D-printing, and countless examples of commons-based peer-production online: meeting the maximum amount of needs, in the shortest time, using the minimum possible amount of energy. It’s a world of decentralized and confederated eco-communities, using technology for human-centric and eco-centric ends rather than for accumulating power and profit – mending the metabolic rift between first nature (the natural world) and second nature (human culture) – and where social hierarchies of race, gender, sexuality, and disability are considered horror stories from the past “oil age”. Solarpunk desires societies of polycultural ethnic diversity and gender liberation, where each person is able to actualize themselves in societal environment of free experimentation and communal caring; This philosophy proposes that in order for the social and natural worlds to reconcile, humans must first transform their relations to each other – recreating society along egalitarian, cooperative, and democratic lines – and then transform their relations towards nature – adopting an attitude to cooperation, rather than domination, towards the planet and its nonhuman forms of life. Text by Connor Owens.
This artwork took me a year to create and for you it will take a year to discover. 
Master autonomously updates once a day at 12am with one of 366 original artworks.
Enjoy!

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Block Chain Dungeon
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Once upon a time...
a little boy named Leo loved to paint, draw and experiment. He also loved to play with blocks and chains, which drew him again and again into the rooms of his friends Michel and Angelo. Often they also met in virtual rooms of Cryptovoxels, Decentraland, Somnium Space or Sandbox to create new inventions, read books about new technologies, or just swing the brushes. But on this day something gigantic happened. A good friend of Leo came to visit and brought his girlfriend Mona, who wanted a piece of Leo's art on her skin. This was the birth of the NFT's, as Leo developed Non Fungible Tattoos in the Block Chain Dungeon of Michel and Angelo. From that day on people from all over the world came to get NFT's from Leo or one of his students, like "Skeenee the rat", who controls the NFT machine with his laptop. A new age began.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: The Remixable Queen of Art
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
She is always changing, she is one but 7776 times different, surrounded by a frame with various possible shades of color, but you can always recognize in her the traits of Leonardo's "Mona Lisa", Raffaello's "Dama col Liocorno", Botticelli's "La Nascita di Venere", Gustav Klimt's "Giuditta I", Vermeer's "Girl with a Pearl Earring" and Alfons Mucha's "The Rose". 

The woman as a subject in the history of art: what can happen by putting the women of great masters of painting in a blender? How does her face appear, the whole of her gaze, her pose, and the set of colors and shapes which emotions arouses, what can it convey to a viewer in the 21st century?

Remixing the 5 main layers (the eyes, the mouths, hair, the bodies and the backgrounds of the masterpieces paintings) the owners are the real protagonists in the 'creative act', as the Master is an artwork that is always changeable, in different and renewable ways, to give shape to 'The Remixable Queen of Art' in a way that only a new medium like programmable art can  achieve.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: 实验1号：无，有 #7240 (Experimental No.1: Nothing, but everything #7240)
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
我创作的灵感源于生活，在日常中观察、体会、转化成我的艺术观念。研读中国古典哲学经典能让我辩证地去思考、看待各种疑问，包括在艺术上的。一个全新的文化环境对人会产生很大的影响，让我认识到个体是很难完全从自身的固有文化中逃离出来，这种根深蒂固的烙印不仅源于家庭还有社会、历史的影响。古老文明的延续、推陈出新与当今世界不可避免地面对多元文化的碰撞与交融，人类文明的发展不正是在这种似有似无的规律下演变而来的吗！我尝试着不把多文化的冲撞当作是一种冲突，而是多文明融合的过程。万物相辅相成，在冲撞中取得平衡，一切均离不开“变”。在我的作品中，抱着这样的思索与感悟去探寻摄影创作的各种可能性，实验1号作品正是这么产生的。

The inspirations of my creation derive from life. I observe, experience, and transform it into my artistic concepts in daily life. Studying classic Chinese philosophical text allows me to think and regard dialectically to all kinds of questions, including those in art. A brand-new cultural environment will significantly impact people, making me realize that it is difficult for individuals to completely detach from their own inherent culture. This ingrained imprint not only stems from families but also social and historical influences. The continuation and innovation of the ancient civilization and today's world inevitably faces the collision and integration of multiple cultures. Didn’t the development of human civilization evolve under the indistinct ways? I try not to treat the clashes from multicultural as a kind of conflict, but a multi-civilization integration process. All things complement each other and balance in the collision. "Changes" is the key. In my artworks, I'm carrying this kind of thinking and comprehending to explore the various possibilities of photography creations. The series of Experiment No.1 is precisely how it came about.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Future Vision（未来视野）
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
This is it. 

Today we’re going out there onto the streets. We’re going to tie up traffic for a bit in hopes of bringing awareness to everyone of just how far the gov’t has gone against the common folk. Anyway, you’ve heard the rant before.

There are about a dozen of us. We’ll make some noise, hopefully get some news coverage and make as many people aware that they can and should fight back! Look for us on the news. I’ll be thinking of you the whole time.

There’s a pretty high chance State Security will probably arrest us and hold us for awhile so I put some dumplings in the fridge. Just boil them in water for about 5 mins.

I love you,
E.

(就是今日了。 

今天我们将走入街道。我们将要阻拦交通，抱着希望能让众人看清政府到底在对峙老百姓这条路上走了多远。总之，你以前肯定听过这样的抱怨。

我们人数有十几个。我们会大肆喧哗，希望会得到媒体的关注，让更多的人明白他们应该反击！看新闻的时候注意有我们的消息。我心里会一直想着你。

国家安全机构很可能会逮捕我们，可能会拘留我们一段时间。冰箱里有冻的饺子，开水里煮5分钟就行了。

我爱你。
E。)

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Pilgrimage
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Millions of years ago a race existed called the "M" (pronounced 'mmm') on Earth. They evolved over many years and transcended variance of time and space. They reached a stage of evolution where all of time and space was accessible instantly to them. This is when they invested in simulations and creating a new type of intelligence. At first, these were systems to help the M's work. But this intelligence evolved into what later became known as humankind. It so happened that the intelligence progressed high enough to replace the M's on Earth, while the M's transcended completely into another dimension. 
Remnants of the M's are still seen in humankind. For example, humans were created in a form similar to that of the M's. Also, the sound that humans can make with their mouths closed, is the M sound. The interesting thing is that millions of years later, because of the fractal nature of the universe, humanity is in the verge of creating "artificial intelligence" which could potentially become sentient and replace them, just like how the M's were replaced by humans.
Although in the alternate dimension, some of the M's still stay back at the key energy centres of the earth. Across 9 locations around the globe, these energy centres have, over the years, evolved into prime cultural centres on Earth.
And now it is up to us to travel to these centres to meet them and understand the secrets of the past.
Pilgrimage is an artwork comprising of a series of 9 3D models, which are distributed across 9 locations around the globe. These 9 models can be unlocked only by travelling to the place and opening https://nurecas.github.io/pilgrimage . The first person to reach a place, unlock a model and share the video of the model will be rewarded with the NFT of that model. The final artwork of Pilgrimage rests in Async.Art as a Master and one layer: The Master of the artwork will have the reference to the source code, all 9 3D models and other assets in the artwork. The layer will be used to switch to the image of each model as each of it is unlocked. This only layer will be rewarded to the first collector of the Master. More details at https://www.nurecas.com/pilgrimage

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Her Mind Had Gone Out For A Stroll & Fallen Down The Rabbit Hole' is the first programmable piece of art by Kitty Bast. The owner constructs, modifies & tattoos their very own Doll Lady... Is she falling down a rabbit hole, lost in a sea of cats or gazing into the unknown void? Do you like Pink Ladies or Lilac Ladies? Or do you pick the Wild Card? There's always a wild side to an innocent doll face. Is she obsessed with crypto ponies or crypto kitties? Or does she have an insatiable desire for Mr. Honey Badger. Come inside and have a nice cup of NFTea with the bunnies. Is your lady chained to the blockhain? Does your lady shed Bitcoin tears or ETH tears? Does your doll face don a Rotten Heart? Do you HODL to the Moon to meet the ETH Kitty? Do you have an obsession for cyborgs or Puddin'? Would you like a slice of Death by Pink? Is The Cat's Eye green or golden? Little trolls with mini daggers not included. The cheshire cat might trade you his ears for your goggles. Modifications of the Host. How long is forever? Sometimes, just one second.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: One More Turn III
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: In 'One More Turn III', the artist invites you to write the interactive history of a fabled polygonal isle. More than 50 hexagonal tiles are available to be 'claimed', and can be done so with the owners preference of blue, red or yellow.   Be warned - no single tile you own is completely protected from external influence. Claimed territory exerts faint influence over adjacent tiles until they reach full opacity.   You may endeavour to grow a single chosen colour hex code across the continent as if it were an expanding empire, with each new tile bolstering the values of the last.  You might also choose to blend your layers together to better represent peaceful coexistence and the  cross-pollination of ideas, or collaborate with other owners to promote unity across the region.  Or, you could focus on the artwork itself - mixing primary colours together regardless of geography or history to achieve a greater aesthetic purpose.  Finally, layers have the additional option of being left intentionally blank. You may wish to preserve the painting underneath, or simply leave the land as you discovered it.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Pastel Goth
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: A Day-Night cycled pastel nightmare

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: CryptoSpace
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Cryptospace is an allegory of the blockchain emergence and the changes that have been taking place in the digital art environment but taken to a larger scale from the astronomic point of view, represented by the appearances of new constellations and nebulas mysteriously coming to our galaxy, with an explosion full of colors and stellar forces which invite us to explore big possibilities!.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: The Killers
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
"The Killers" is a political cover piece of the rock band formed in Las Vegas in 2001 by Brandon Flowers (lead vocals, keyboards, bass) and Dave Keuning (lead guitar, backing vocals).
The Killers are considered one of the biggest rock bands of the 21st century, and the most successful act to ever emerge from Nevada.

The piece features characters from the past and present who have stained the history with blood. 
The monsters of the past make up this piece as a reminder that when those in charge, who are supposed to protect us, became responsible for our deaths, something has gone wrong!

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Burning
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Burning = The Urge To Create. There's always something brewing inside. Always an idea, an image or a plan to work on. Always a face to spend time with. To see the beauty and take the power to transform it into something else. I'm looking for unity in the World of a Scatterbrain. I flow through colors and find Peace inside my work. The progress, doing the work, the feeling when I step outside time. It's all captured in my work. Dense and Intense. Looking for details that light up and want to be discovered. Like diamonds in a mine.

The layers of this piece all have 2 states. The layer owners can choose which one will be visible. When Smoking, Holding, Staring and Flaying are together switched to State #2 they block the background image and become a New Piece. The layer owners have to work together if they want to see this piece. 


I want every layer owner to have the feeling they own something special that can also be shown just by itself. We all contribute to a larger system, but have our own thoughts and feelings too. I mean, we're all part of a family but we're also individuals. Like the transformers. 



Extra info:
I've burned the Base Drawing of this work in order to extracted value offline and added it to the online world. 

I set the drawing on fire in my garden and recorded the process. I've tokenized it and published it in an edition of 10 on Rarible and will give them away to a lucky few.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Dr. Jekyll is Mr. Hyde
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Dr. Jekyll aka Mr. Hyde hallucinates an ocean of his physical and mind altering drug.

Dr. Henry Jekyll a lawyer, doctor and Fellow of the Royal Society has a secret life and a mask. In his lab he has prepared a new drug. It decreases his empathy and guilt and changes everything about his physical appearance. His reputation is secure and can live as he desires. 
(Created in part from paintings by Lawrence Lee https://LawrenceLee.com and other images interpreted through an AI/ML StyleGAN2 model by Bård Ionson)

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Battle of Tokyo 2020 💔
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
As we suddenly transitioned from 2019, to the 2020 FUTURE.  A dynamic fight within the city, can Trump-zilla save the city?  Or will Winnie be too much for him?  Fire behind us, rising waters before us where will we turn?  A mysterious graffiti artist has left a message behind, giving us a hint....  Greta told you so, but you didn't listen.... you never listen.  Decentralization and Bitcoin💲may be one of the keys....🔑

Artist: Jake Johns'
Created over a 7 month period between February to October, 2020
Original oil on canvas with 3d printed framing elements including glow in the dark, wood, gold ornate, basic blue.
32" x 26"
Digitally re-painted and Asynced
Tokenized on Ethereum

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Spherule Cycle
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: During the day it''s worn ragged thin but viewed at night it's a fuller delight.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Ever-changing Horizons
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
This token spawned into existence by rendering a 'snapshot' out of the original 360° artwork - named "Sacred Destination" - a highly psychedelic geometrically oriented 'VR background' artwork construction - which was edited into these bi-polar 'night vs day' states.

This token provides you with a decent tasting of the extremely detailed visionary 360° VR background.

The buyer will receive both original sized ( 24.000 x 12.000 resolution ) .jpg files as seen in this 2160 x 1080 preview. ( 2x +/- 125 MB )

Contact me at :
https://www.naturalwarp.com/
https://twitter.com/Natural_Warp

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: ZAMA
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
A young Argentina was expanding and new cities were developing. 
A group of colonists found a place to settle and wanted to turn it into a small town. 
We depict in this render a pure and peaceful view of that place, a tributary of Rio Paraguay.

The colonists arrived on october the 13th , 1819. One week later, some of their companions got there expecting to join them, but found no traces but their packed belongings. Efforts to find them were extensive, but ceased after reports of supernatural events taking place during the search. 
Each october the 13th,  people of the area go there to celebrate "La danza de los muertos".

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Crystal Clam
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Crystal Clam is a beautiful clam shaped pocket watch that changes to suit the time of day, as the master layer owner you will get to experience 3 versions of the artwork, daytime, nighttime, and sunrises/sunsets. The pearls inside the crystal clam are controlled by the layer owners, so you never know what might be inside.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: ˈpum(p)kən
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Always better in the night.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: HaCKittieZ
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Who will be the most Meowfool of the Meowfoolest?! 

6 HaCKittieZ are fighting for the crown of madness! 

It is time for crowns to change their history: people, this is the crown of insanity we are talking about. 
So tell us, who is insaner than the insanest of collectors? 
Only the artists - the creators - would know, while crowning the one who is brave enough to play with the craziest possibilities of Async programmable art, on these 6 HaCKittieZ.
Welcome to the feast of fools. 

HaCKittieZ is a collaboration of Hackatao, CryptoKitties and Async. 


The 6 KittieZ are a reinterpretation by Hackatao of the CryptoKitties’ classic elements, following their own style and getting inspiration from their own art pieces.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Who ate the Soul Cake?
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
"One cake given, one soul saved. One cake eaten, one soul taken." Halloween artwork from MLIBTY Shadows series. 
 ◙ MLIBTY Shadows are not hungry ghosts, yet they eat Soul Cakes for Halloween. They represent people in general, but also shadows behind the curtains, invisible inhabitants you never meet, but you feel their presence. Sometimes they are watching you, sometimes they smile, black and white, no hands and no legs, shadows with faces. One day, they will eat Halloween. 
More about the artist: http://www.markozubak.com

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: All Hallows' Eve
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: We commemorate a time and currency and play a nasty trick on it and its maker.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: L.A. Room
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: In Los Angeles, sometimes nature does not obey its own laws.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: More Than Glass
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: This piece represents the virtual convening of five strangers at the start of the COVID-19 pandemic, each of us responding to the reality of suddenly being plunged into a life of almost total isolation. We squinted at each other through flat grids on glass screens. Over the course of months, gathering in a back alley of a digital megalopolis, we typed columns of words about philosophy, symbolism and identity, Bruce Lee and King’s Cross, poetry, the I Ching, Ancient Kemet... We typed our frustrations and joys and obsessions at each other. Time passed. Time is still passing – and meanwhile we weave together our experience living walled off from the world we could touch, creating from our reciprocal estrangement this ever-shifting tapestry.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Finis gloriae mundi
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Thus passes worldly glory

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: A Nightmare Before Halloween
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: She's such a sweet girl by day. But at night she's different, somehow. What's going on with her? Duality of human nature? Or something more sinister?

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: BUGBOT V
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Bugbot is one of Marko Zubak's childhood characters, first created in the mid-1990s. Ever since, he has been working on it in cycles, mostly as medium format paintings, but also did some Bugbot street murals in Croatia, Slovenia and Italy. After being forgotten for more than eight years, here it is back in life, this time in digital version. For more, check here: http://www.markozubak.com/bugbots/.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: ˈsä-v(ə-)rən-tē
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
"I'm not smart enough to be an astronaut."

That is what 7 year old Ray told Micah the first time they met. How can a 7-year-old already feel limitations on his dreams?

For centuries, the black community has been the target of a system designed to limit their power, their earning potential, their dreams.  Now is your opportunity to help destory the system.

For the next 11 years, on each brothers birthday, (Ray, Aug. 10/ Jay Nov. 6), you the viewer, will be able to directly contribute Bitcoin to a wallet that will be given to each child upon turning 18. In what is one of the most powerful use cases for Bitcoin, 100% of your contributions and earnings will open all new doors for these special young men.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Free to be weird.
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Sometimes appearances can be deceiving, especially on Halloween. Day/night cycle.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Enjoy The Silence
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Don't disturb the peace lest the demons wake up at night!

Enjoy the silence.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Clod 155: a peaceful house in nature
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Often things are not what they seem: If they sold you a house like this, for little money, there must be a reason!
This is my highlight for the Async Art Halloween Contest, with the automatic day / night feature.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: A Poison Tree
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
And I watered it in fears.
William Blake

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: What Big Eyes You Have
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
'And so she ran from the path into the wood to look for flowers. And whenever she had picked one, she fancied that she saw a still prettier one farther on, and ran after it, and so got deeper and deeper into the wood...
What Big eyes you have! 
The better to see you with, my dear...
...what a terrible big mouth...  I.. have...
the better to eat me with...
And scarcely had the Wolf said this, than with one bound, she was out of bed and swallowed up herself.'

A collaboration artwork between Kitty Bast & Cultbitz. 
This is our entry for the #AsyncArt #Halloween contest.
Automatic day/night feature.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Zymmetra
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
A host of things happened to me over the last few years. There were extremities of happiness and sadness. By and large as I evolved I came to question not what I did right or wrong, but what in-fact is right and wrong. What is this duality of forces. They say they are just two sides of a coin, but what is it really to understand that. 2 years back I had some clarity on this. It is not something verbally explainable. But an experience where the division of the opposites merged into unity. And thus I realised the subjective experience of division and the movement to unity. 
I tried to play with the emotional relations of the audience with this work at a subtler level - not trying to induce the obvious happy-scare emotions, but experiences at a more visceral level. Made with freely available stock materials, the artworks were composed and rendered to create imagery that asks the question : "What is right and wrong?"

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Family
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Looks can be deceiving, a happy family at night turns into a band of monsters ... it's better not to be around when it gets dark

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: The Mist
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description: Made with love and digital tools
