0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: 'Attack'
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
An abstract study based on the understanding of the ADSR envelope and its underlying principles of 'Attack, Decay, Sustain & Release'.

My ideas are borne in midflight on ethereal planes of existence and brought into life within the first impulse. We have to strike when creativity hits, when the gift of the ultra present presents itself to us or watch it drift off into the ether.

'Attack' is the first in the series of 4 works and features a 24hr cycle of 24 artworks.
It is inspired by the minimalist aesthetic of Japanese Ukiyo-e prints and my fascination with fragmented forms.
Created using 3D techniques, 2D illustration methods and zero AI. 

Future enhancements include AR connectivity that provide access to original audio compositions and more.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Turris Aquae
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Flying jellyfish, ravenous bird plants, and gravity-defying submarines, emerged from the deep waters of Spelunca Mons, A.K.A. Cave Mountain. The council decreed a tower city be built to observe and guard the realm against the fearsome magical creatures. But night after night, and day after day, the creatures that poured forth from the caves beneath the water amazed the city folk. They did not plague the nearby villages and they did not attack a soul. They moved with elegance and purpose.

The caves were never understood. Nor were they explored by those living in the city above. However, they continued to spawn all sorts of magical beings. Before long, Turris Aquae became a place of healing. The waters were considered holy, the creatures considered good, and the fish were delicacies exported to realms far and wide.

This NFT changes how it looks based on the time of day. It has a different image for day, night, sunrise, and sunset.
Size: 2160 × 3840px.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Jellyfish
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
Jellyfish are very ancient animals.

Jellyfish fossils have been found dating back more than 550 million years ago (Cambrian period), 250 million years before dinosaurs appeared on earth.

Some of them are considered eternal animals, being able to transform themselves from jellyfish to polyps, in an eternal life cycle.

When man and all other animals will be extinct on earth, jellyfish will be the only living beings that will populate our planet and, perhaps, will also learn to fly, living not only in the water but also in the air.

And when jellyfish sleep, they often dream of music...


Jellyfish is a project in 3 parts :

- 3 music NFTs published on Makersplace : https://makersplace.com/wayang/gallery/created

- 1 NFT formed by 24 images that changes during the 24 hours of the day, published on Async art

(GMT -5.00) Eastern US and Canada timezone.  Based on the GMT offset and does not take into account daylight savings.  AI art 1024 x 1024 px.

0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.name: Shadows of the Surreal
0xb6dae651468e9593e4581705a09c10a76ac1e0.description:
These 24 dark surreal artworks by Winchawa capture the essence of the enigmatic and the ethereal, drawing you into a labyrinth of shifting shadows and elusive forms.

As you immerse yourself in these dark and captivating artworks, you find yourself caught between realms, where reality intertwines with the ethereal and shadows take on a life of their own.

Shadows cascade and merge, shaping the contours of a surreal landscape that defies conventional understanding. 

It is as if the very fabric of reality is being stretched and woven anew with each passing hour.

Every passing hour brings a profound transformation to Shadows of the Surreal. 

This NFT evolves before your very eyes, revealing new dimensions and hidden symbols that speak to the depths of your soul. 

The dynamic nature of the artwork mirrors the ever-shifting nature of existence, constantly challenging your perceptions and inviting introspection.

Shadows of the Surreal is an invitation to embrace the unknown, to question the boundaries of reality, and to delve into the depths of your own imagination.

 It whispers secrets, leaving trails of intrigue in its wake, and ignites a fire within you to explore the uncharted territories of your mind.

Shadows of the Surreal promises an unforgettable journey, where the shadows come alive, the surreal becomes tangible, and your perception of the world is forever transformed.
